tag plugins may tag a single given file ,e.g. read exif tags or result in
tagging other files ,e.g. reading tvshow.nfo.

tag plugins may also look for the original file for auxilary infos (like
searching for a given .mkv for the same name .nfo .

plugins may listen to a given mimetype or a case-insensitive filename. once
triggered they will get the filename relative from the cwd.
